          <aside class="ux code">
            <h3>Solution</h3>
            <p>
              My team and I designed an simple web application that uploads any CSV files, then it processes these CSV data into a 3D visualization by using D3.js and x3dom. The visualization provides the ability to zoom in/out, click and drag to any angle that the user wishes to see.
            </p>
